}, Open  ]],

Cell["\<\
Sometimes, it is useful to generalize the condition number and define it to \
be the ratio of the maximum singular value to the minimum non-zero singular \
value:\
\>", "ExampleText",
 CellID->1594946195,ExpressionUUID->"d07c42fa-425d-4c2f-ab94-b89a39826b23"],

Cell[CellGroupData[{

Cell[BoxData[
